snippet.title: Highway Police Simulator | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
COMING to PC, PS5 and XBOX SERIES X|S on 5 December 2024

Immerse yourself in the authentic police work of the American Highway Patrol. Solve cases, chase criminals and explore the open-world. Choose your officer and tackle the everyday life on the highways. Will you be able to maintain law and order? 

For more news and information follow us: 
Discord: https://discord.gg/QMqGJ3nuhu
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/highwaypolicesimulator
